==電影製作==
===初衷===
橫跨三大洲，“Sign Gene”在日本、美國和義大利取景、拍攝。 [[Emilio_Insolera|艾米利歐・殷索萊拉]]起初以一部短片開始構思，但主題引起了廣大的興趣，使得殷索萊拉相信這部電影有可能獲得更大的製作並吸引更多的觀眾。他將劇本重寫為超過70分鐘長篇電影。<ref name="kansai scene">{{cite web|url=https://www.kansaiscene.com/2009/12/emilio-insolera/|title=Emilio Insolera|date=1 December 2009|publisher=|accessdate=2017-04-09|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402105555/https://www.kansaiscene.com/2009/12/emilio-insolera/|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於殷索萊拉希望此電影能由聾人演員和手語母語者演出，大部份的演員都是透過熟人介紹獲得參與機會。這部電影的設計有[[昆汀·塔倫提諾|昆汀·塔倫提諾]]和[[羅伯特·羅德里格兹|羅伯特·羅德里格兹]]的元素。<ref name="The Games Machine">{{cite web|url=https://www.thegamesmachine.it/cinema-e-serie-tv/73937/sign-gene-supereroi-sordi/|title=Sign Gene è il nuovo film di supereroi sordi|first=|last=The Games Machine|accessdate=20 August 2017|publisher=''[[The_Games_Machine|The Games Machine]]''|date=27 March 2017|language=it|archive-date=2018-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180830041319/https://www.thegamesmachine.it/cinema-e-serie-tv/73937/sign-gene-supereroi-sordi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===歷史，文化和語言參考===
''Sign Gene''對聾人歷史，聾人文化和手語語言學進行了幾次編碼。 Q.I.A.代表QuinPar Intelligence Agency，QuinPar是指五個參數，即手語語言學中形成符號的語音成分：手形，運動，位置，方向和非手動信號。特工Tom Clerc 的姓氏取自聾人歷史上著名人物的姓氏，勞倫特克萊克，一位為美國手語的聾教育家。1.8.8.0則是取自1880年在意大利[[米蘭|米蘭]]舉行的第二屆聾人教育國際大會。大會決議將手語從聾人教育中剔除“。<ref name="Pacific Standard">{{Cite web |url=https://psmag.com/social-justice/sign-language-is-a-superpower |title=When Sign Language Is a Superpower |website=psmag.com |access-date=17 September 2018 |archive-date=2018-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617065752/https://psmag.com/social-justice/sign-language-is-a-superpower |dead-url=no }}</ref> Figures such as Alexander Graham Bell and Jean Massieu are present in the film as well.<ref name="LATimes">{{Cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-capsule-sign-gene-review-20180412-story.html |title=Inventive 'Sign Gene' chronicles derring-do of first deaf superheroes |website=latimes.com |access-date=17 September 2018 |archive-date=2018-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023155406/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-capsule-sign-gene-review-20180412-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

